issue.title: Repeated warning: dataset </supercontig_0/continuous> cannot be read, deflate filter is not available from genomedata-load

content.raw:
Does this happen when `/home/mkarimzadeh/Documents/RunSegwayProtocol/Data/GenomeDataArchives/ENCFF151DIJ_MM.1S_H3K4me3.genomedata` does not already exist?
